narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Lh Wellbeing Care INC is a Health Maintenance Organization provider based in New York, NY. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $76.3M in Medicaid payments across 552K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $76.3M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
